<h3 id="doc-responsive-variants">Responsive Variants</h3>
<p>Available breakpoints:</p>
<ul>
<li><code>sm</code> ≥ 40rem</li>
<li><code>md</code> ≥ 48rem</li>
<li><code>lg</code> ≥ 64rem</li>
<li><code>xl</code> ≥ 80rem</li>
<li><code>xxl</code> ≥ 96rem</li>
</ul>
<p>Pattern: <code>.d-[breakpoint]-[value]</code></p>
<table>
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 30%" />
<col style="width: 69%" />
</colgroup>
<thead>
<tr class="header">
